snippet.title: Paul Blart: Mall Cop - Mall Maze (Full Gameplay No Deaths)
snippet.description:
Full playthrough of this short Pac-Man clone tie-in to Paul Blart.
The English version of this doesn't appear to have been archived, but it's the same game in Russian.
You can play this yourself using the Flashpoint Archive.
